videos.description: Marcus Foster finds space for the 3-pointer to expand Creighton's early lead.
videos.headline: Foster gets Blue Jays up early with 3

videos.description: Ty-Shon Alexander scrambles for a loose ball and converts a fantastic reverse lay-in.
videos.headline: Alexander hits crazy reverse for Creighton

videos.description: Mitchell Ballock follows up his missed 3-pointer by stealing the rebound from UCLA and finishing at the rim for Creighton.
videos.headline: Ballock gets the steal and score

videos.description: Khyri Thomas lobs a long ball for Martin Krampelj, who brings down the alley-oop with two hands for Creighton.
videos.headline: Krampelj slams home alley-oop

videos.description: Creighton's Martin Krampelj finds space under the net and draws the foul from Thomas Welsh on the layup.
videos.headline: Krampelj gets behind net for and-1
